    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>貴様の中の欲望は
貪欲に膨らみ続けるのだっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The avarice continues to
grow inside you bastards!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体にぽっかり空いた虚無なる
穴はどれだけ、その愛を
吸っても満ちるに足りねぇ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are empty and hollow. Your desire for
"Love" is your sole motivation to keep going.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check pls</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、何言ってんだ、
こいつ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nothing he says makes any sense to me...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>理解する必要はねぇのさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There is no need to understand any of it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここでおまえたちは、その虚無に
飲み込まれるんだからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I will devour you...your nihilism and
everything else in its entirety...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272252</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>来るよ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-It's coming...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
